<i>a nut-scented alien,</i>

275
00:22:54,605 --> 00:22:56,945
<i>They meet and the heart beats faster.</i>

276
00:23:00,405 --> 00:23:05,405
<i>Sparkle, sparkle, the galaxy's a popcorn shower.</i>

277
00:23:07,745 --> 00:23:11,915
<i>Yesterday goes bye, bye, bye, (Gohan),</i>

278
00:23:11,955 --> 00:23:16,045
<i>Mystery, (far as the eye can see),</i>

279
00:23:16,085 --> 00:23:19,555
<i>Gather up your energy, (substitutes are okay),</i>

280
00:23:19,595 --> 00:23:22,175
<i>Come over here, lai, lai, lai.</i>

281
00:23:23,925 --> 00:23:29,685
<i>Ooh, miracle ZENKAI power!</i>

282
00:23:31,935 --> 00:23:33,775
<i>A hungry, naughty Kinto Un,</i>

283
00:23:33,815 --> 00:23:35,605
<i>A mountain full of horizons.</i>

284
00:23:35,645 --> 00:23:39,615
<i>They meet each other, they come apart,</i>
<i>they meet each other, they come apart, Oh, no!</i>

285
00:23:39,655 --> 00:23:45,285
<i>Aah, enough! Even Kami-sama has it rough.</i>

286
00:23:45,325 --> 00:23:47,455
<i>So sorry.</i>

287
00:23:47,495 --> 00:23:52,585
<i>Ooh, full-bellied ZENKAI power!</i>

288
00:23:55,335 --> 00:24:00,635
<i>Come on out, full-on ZENKAI power!</i>

289
00:24:12,265 --> 00:24:14,395
<i>Heya! I'm Goku!</i>

290
00:24:14,435 --> 00:24:16,605
<i>I'm going to train in the Next World,</i>

291
00:24:16,645 --> 00:24:19,405
<i>but I'll come visit once in a while,</i>
<i>so keep your chin up, Gohan.</i>

292
00:24:19,445 --> 00:24:22,235
<i>Hey, you don't have to</i>
<i>worry about what's to come.</i>

293
00:24:22,275 --> 00:24:25,575
<i>I mean, he is your son, after all.</i>

294
00:24:25,615 --> 00:24:27,615
<i>Next time on Dragon Ball Z,</i>

295
